Primary dropdown options:
- Add Process → shows: text field (Process Name, placeholder "P1"), 
  number input (Pages, 1–32), green "Create" button
- Kill Process → shows: dropdown populated with currently active process 
  names from live SSE state, red "Kill" button
- Set Algorithm → shows: three pill radio buttons: FIFO / LRU / OPT. 
  Clicking one applies immediately (POST "algo fifo/lru/opt" to /command), 
  no confirm button needed
