- Below 50%: red text + red progress bar
- 50–75%: amber text + amber bar
- Above 75%: green text + green bar

Below the percentage, add a one-line plain English interpretation 
that updates live:
- Below 50%: "High fault rate — memory is under pressure"
- 50–75%: "Moderate performance — some unnecessary loads occurring"  
